o&#328;at we zy&yacute;anly &ccedil;i&#351;lerini bejermegi&#328; esasy
usullaryndan biridir.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;any&#328; g&ouml;wr&uuml;mi we usuly
&yacute;a&yacute;ramagy&#328; derejesi, &ouml;s&uuml;&#351;i&#328; tebigaty we
&ccedil;i&#351;i&#328; lez&yacute;onyny&#328; lokalizasi&yacute;asy bilen
kesgitlen&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Ownuk &ccedil;i&#351;ler bilen, endoskopiki
a&yacute;yrmak &yacute;a-da &ccedil;i&#351;i&#328; bir b&ouml;legini&#328;
